Bakge Libraries
===============

If you're on Linux you'll need to install required libraries.

Install GLFW 2.7.9 on Linux
 - Download GLFW from http://www.glfw.org
 - Extract and enter the directory
 - Run $ sudo make x11 x11-install


Get GLFW 2.7.9 on Windows
If you're on Windows, download the Win32 binaries archive and extract include and lib-* folders to bakge/lib/glfw-2.7.9/
